{"type": "article", "id": 9395, "title": "广告狂人快结束了，他们成了麦肯的“新员工”", "description": "Sterling Cooper 的未来在曼哈顿第三大道 622 号得以延续", "date": "2015-05-11T08:21:52Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 8252, "name": "《广告狂人》"}, {"id": 9897, "name": "麦肯"}, {"id": 9898, "name": "McCANN"}, {"id": 9005, "name": "Don Draper"}, {"id": 9899, "name": "Roger Sterling"}, {"id": 9900, "name": "Peggy Olson"}, {"id": 9901, "name": "John Holloway"}], "category": 3, "author": 103970, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 28, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160604222607BI5wMYuC1zonifch.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t麦肯（McCANN）最终还是并购了 SC&amp;P（<span style=\"color:#252525;font-family:sans-serif;font-size:14.399999618530273px;line-height:17.600000381469727px;white-space:normal;\">Sterling Cooper &amp; Partners）</span>。<span style=\"font-size:15.833333015441895px;line-height:31.992185592651367px;\">随着经典美剧《广告狂人》（Mad Man）即将完结，</span>这一剧中虚构的广告公司真的成为了麦肯世界集团旗下的 “一员” 。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160604222602OGaRV0Zhx19oXT4A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t还记得当初 Sterling Cooper 差点就被卖给麦肯吗？员工们都一脸嫌弃地表示不想去，并以此契机创造了一家真正属于自己的公司。然而<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:宋体;font-size:14.399999618530273px;line-height:17.600000381469727px;white-space:pre-wrap;\">折腾到第七季的这些主角们，如今在完成收购后，纷纷成为了麦肯的新“员工”。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#3E3E3E;font-family:宋体;font-size:14.399999618530273px;line-height:17.600000381469727px;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604222603lZhp4BHJi5tgvCFu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.765\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604222603qh9u6C2joOgHMBv7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.715\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604222604gavDqru915sjdGPU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604222604fbP3Gar59XtMgqiL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604222605YrsViGfP9wAOFLgx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">作为在剧中屡次被提及的真实存在的 4A 广告公司——麦肯世界集团，最近很“贴心”地为这些新员工设计了名片、工牌，以及位于曼哈顿第三大道的纽约总部办公大楼下张贴的巨幅欢迎海报。最“贴心”的是，他们还帮人家把新公司的 Logo 也设计好了，真是操碎了心。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606042226058G27efmYkKLBsZHb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:15.8333330154419px;line-height:31.9921855926514px;white-space:pre-wrap;\">十年摸爬滚打，当初的菜鸟 Peggy Oisen 来到麦肯，已经完全蜕变成了资深大咖。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604222605QHv1YWhMIpET5c7O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604222606dNyvGO8xt903zrjP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79201102\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span><span style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">归功于围绕该剧在 Twitter 上的互动，“麦肯”在社交媒体上的提及率提升了 46%。</span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}